{"tid":2137033,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人自細同兄弟姊妹相依為命","createTime":"2020-08-02T14:48:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-07T12:16:17.000Z","uid":199804,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"8f7c9742b6082967b4db237a35a6f8788f692858","tid":2137033,"uid":199804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T14:48:23.000Z","msg":"我有個男性朋友，由細到大父母都成日要出國公幹，長時間得個啊嫲同啊妹喺屋企。佢個啊嫲都好好人，知道冇人照顧兩個細蚊仔，會幫手做吓家務，但老人家實在郁動唔到太多，所以大部分煮飯清潔嗰啲都係啊哥(我朋友)同啊妹做翻。而且啊嫲都唔係喺嗰度住，夜晚晚飯前就會番自己屋企，所以得翻兩兄妹喺屋企。聽到都覺得寂寞。。。"},{"pid":"e051dc046115822ca3917e809f54cb02f5f80cd0","tid":2137033,"uid":199804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T15:10:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64a766820d84ef8607be0960aaa5e6a9ece1ba52","tid":2137033,"uid":146299,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T15:27:35.000Z","msg":"又你朋友。。"},{"pid":"abcfceffd7a899145e778aff1609416e0a016f20","tid":2137033,"uid":234509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T16:05:03.000Z","msg":"你的朋友=你"},{"pid":"0b5ec755822dae08b8dbb8b3fcd8a079dd059e0a","tid":2137033,"uid":23655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T12:11:27.000Z","msg":"。"},{"pid":"6d26dd36a3594acdcf54583566fb9516e8ac12b4","tid":2137033,"uid":245484,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T12:16:17.000Z","msg":"起碼有兩兄妹, 唔算寂寞啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}